had taken, and kept coming. As McGowan tryed to push, Forrior grabbed at
that arm in a attempt to twist the arm, and bring it down on his
shoulder.

As Depp punches, Hot Rod grabs at the arm, trying to twist it. He would
then kick up, whitch would force the arm to bend the wrong way.
